sentences: Mariama Goodman (born 26 October 1977) is an English dancer and singer who is currently a member of girl group Honeyz.
Goodman began her pop career in 1996 signed to Jive Records in the United States with Solid HarmoniE. The group had the same management as, and toured regularly with, 'N Sync and the Backstreet Boys.
The group disbanded in 2000 but reunited (without Goodman) in 2013.
